      "content": "A respite... yes, exactly. A release from everything. I find myself looking at the heavy velvet curtains, or the deep, dark waters of the lake beyond the garden, and I feel a strange pull. It's as if they are calling me to step out of this play and into the stillness. If one were to choose to depart, to truly find that peace you speak of, how would one even begin to make such a graceful exit?",
